description:
&lt;p&gt;The Hillingdon Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust is looking to appoint a dynamic and motivated Theatres store operative, to support our Materials Officer in Theatres across Hillingdon and Mount Vernon.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will oversee the Theatres at both the Hillingdon Hospital and the Mount Vernon Hospital site (Northwood) and is therefore expected to work across both sites. The Theatre suite at Hillingdon Hospital comprises of 7 theatres, Maternity 2 theatres and the Treatment Centre at Mount Vernon has 4 theatres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Theatres store operative will support the Materials Officer who is responsible for maintaining a safe stock level in all theatres across both sites, and to respond to non-stock ordering requirements for the departments. They will be able to demonstrate an ability to on their own initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For informal enquiries please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zoe McDowall, Service Manager for theatres and Anaesthetics for the Division of Surgery and Anaesthetics on 01895 279044&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
